news.title: Revival charges needed to restore cancelled Chandigarh housing board dwelling unit licences
news.para: In case allotment of a dwelling unit is cancelled due to non-payment of license fee, revival charges shall be calculated at 10% of the accumulated outstanding amount of license fee.

news.title: Indore civic body starts verifying building permission documents
news.para: As per civic body officials, an 80ft road has been planned by the civic body on this stretch with an aim to solve traffic jams and congestion problems.

news.title: Urban estate to come up on 2,000 acres in Ludhiana: Punjab housing minister
news.para: Glada is already in the process of acquiring around 2,000-acre site at Ladowal bypass in Bagga Kalan, Noorpur Bet, Garha and Gounspur villages.
